2 (a) The title of the grant;
3 (b) The statute or administrative regulation that authorizes the grant;
4 (c) The posting date of the grant;
5 (d) The deadline for applying for the grant;
6 (e) The eligibility criteria for the grant;
7 (f) The total funds available, including the maximum and minimum amounts a
8 grant recipient could receive;
9 (g) The grantor's contact information; and
10 (h) Any other information that may assist in the identification and orderly
11 allocation of grant funds.
12 (5) Each county and area development district shall display a link to the grant
13 database prominently on the homepage or first page of its website.
